						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the high school compound.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1766, Krōdhi, Śrāvaṇa, ba. 12, Monday</hi> corresponding to 1844 A.D., September 9.</p>						

						<p>It records the gift of a tank by <hi rend="italic">mahānāyaṅkāchārya</hi> Raghunāyakula-nāyuḍu, son of Harivaṁśaṁ Haridāsappa-nāyuḍu of Ghaṭṭu-saṁsthānam and Maṁgamma.</p>						

						</summary>
